app_description: Quality useful application that helps to translate words into English or Chinese with one touch. Perfect for students teachers adults travellers and for anyone who is interested in studying foreign languages. It is a translation tool that helps you break down language barriers. Excellent app for all who make the first steps in learning English or Chinese languages. Intuitive interface easy navigation quick result. Begin conversations confidently!
